company description

why are we here?

you may not know our name but we can guarantee you know our work - all we do has a positive impact on life, health and the environment. eurofins is by your side every day, from the food you eat to the medicines you rely on. we work with the biggest companies in the world, making sure the products they supply are safe, their ingredients are authentic and labelling is accurate. our global and diverse network of companies offers a stimulating start-up environment with fast track careers. as a part of eurofins, you will contribute to making science and innovation happen every day!

job description

how can you contribute?

as part of the it infrastructure support team for eurofins environment testing spain division, you will join a growing international team to support our site in castellón. ideally, you have a minimum of 2 years of experience in hardware and software incident management positions, user support, dealing with suppliers, etc.

we are looking for a proactive, organized, empathetic person with strong communication skills and hands-on involvement. in your role, you are user-oriented and committed in your approach!

as a helpdesk & field technician within our it infrastructure support team, you will:

discuss with hardware and software suppliers;
participate in business application testing;
control department invoicing;
manage o365, powerbi, powerap, teams and sharepoint;
control and take inventory of equipment, users and licenses;
control and manage landlines and mobile telephony;
manage new user and hardware requests;
resolve hardware or software microcomputer incidents;
resolve incidents concerning lan and wifi networks;
install and configure network printers.
